# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->
<meta charset="UTF-8" aria-hidden="false" />
<meta charset="UTF-8" role="meta" />
<html aria-required="true"></html>
<script aria-label="script"></script>
<script role="script"></script>
<style aria-labelledby="id"></style>
<style role="style"></style>
<meta charset="UTF-8" role="meta" aria-hidden="true" />
<meta charset="UTF-8" aria-foo="bar" aria-hidden="true" />
<META charset="UTF-8" role="meta" />
<STYLE ROLE="style"></STYLE>
<SCRIPT ARIA-LABEL="script"></SCRIPT>

```

